            <title>[CASSANDRA-10257] InvertedIndex trigger example has not been updated post 8099</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10257</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;InvertedIndex&lt;/tt&gt; example is still using pre-8099 code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
