                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14729398" author="iamaleksey" created="Thu, 3 Sep 2015 17:02:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s unfortunate, but in no way beta or rc blocking, since it&apos;s just an example. Feel free to volunteer to fix it though.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14939663" author="mike_tr_adamson" created="Thu, 1 Oct 2015 10:43:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=iamaleksey&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;iamaleksey&quot;&gt;iamaleksey&lt;/a&gt; I&apos;ve done a search and can&apos;t find anyone who has successfully managed to get the &lt;tt&gt;InvertedIndex&lt;/tt&gt; example working. The instructions in the README are not intuitive and although it is easy to install and build it is not easy to get it to do what it is meant to do.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Would you object to removing this example and adding a simpler and better documented example that does something like adding entries to an audit table?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14940179" author="iamaleksey" created="Thu, 1 Oct 2015 18:23:31 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Would you object to removing this example and adding a simpler and better documented example that does something like adding entries to an audit table?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Not at all. Still up for doing it?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14940962" author="mike_tr_adamson" created="Fri, 2 Oct 2015 09:34:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, I&apos;ll try and get a patch together in the next couple of days.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14964929" author="mike_tr_adamson" created="Tue, 20 Oct 2015 10:22:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The triggers example is not &lt;tt&gt;AuditTrigger&lt;/tt&gt; and adds a mutation to an audit table containing the keyspace, table &amp;amp; primary key of the update in the trigger.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14998761" author="iamaleksey" created="Tue, 10 Nov 2015 15:38:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;LGTM. Committed as &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/commit/fb463c79e0cb63114a2f220182e7c7ed3e0f4205&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;fb463c79e0cb63114a2f220182e7c7ed3e0f4205&lt;/a&gt; to 3.0 and merged with 3.1 and trunk, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
